gujarati.context:
Brahman bhelaana unghamaa, soota te sadne santaay;
Te ekoekane utaadiya, Prabhu pote jaali baay.

Brahmans mistake in their sleep; 
They awaken to their Lord's mercy.

Here is the translation:

He performed his own yajna, and considered it auspicious; 
That yajna was performed, something fitting was said as told.
